posts.name: Quinton Rodgers
posts.cooked: Do the LED’s blink the same as the rest or is it slightly different. The Falcon’s have multiple orange blinks codes as shown on page 39-42 ( link )

posts.name: Fletch
posts.cooked:
Quint0n53:

for context REV CAN systems starts viewing CAN from the PDH , whereas DS and CTRE start from Rio

All CAN devices are viewed from the perspective of the code trying to communicate over it (i.e. RoboRio).  If you’re referring to what you see in the REV Hardware Client, that’s viewed from the perspective of the device you’re plugged into with USB-C (which could very easily be the PDH , but doesn’t have to be)
